weka.core.converters
Class SASLoader

java.lang.Object
  weka.core.converters.AbstractLoader
      weka.core.converters.AbstractFileLoader
          weka.core.converters.SASLoader
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, BatchConverter, FileSourcedConverter, Loader, EnvironmentHandler, RevisionHandler
public class SASLoader
extends AbstractFileLoader
implements BatchConverter

Reads a source that is in SAS's "sas7bdat" format. Uses the eobjects.org "SassyReader" project: http://sassyreader.eobjects.org.
